@協助開發或導入企業資訊系統
@資訊機房管理及維護運作
@資訊安全管理
@Lims系統之管理及維護
@協助維護IT設施,包括伺服器/防火牆/網路/軟體等
@協助排除使用者日常電腦相關問題

1.網路監控及異常狀況排除;
2.遊戲伺服器監控及維護;
3.伺服器及PC軟硬體架設安裝管理;
4.需白天排班及夜間接On Call(另有津貼補助);
5.SOP文件制作。

JOB DESCRIPTION
- Min 2 years and above experience in IT industry as developer/release related roles;
- Hands-on experience in SVN, Hudson/Jenkins, branching/ merging practical skills;
- Basic Knowledge of development in core Java, J2EE, Oracle or other relational database and SQL scripting, Javascript;
- At least one scripting language (shell, Perl, Python, etc);
- Good technical writing skills;
- Fluent in English; 
JOB DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES
- Work with developers and supporting team to sustain release process efficiently;
- Follow the release processes and policy strictly;
- Conduct release conflicts review with developers to ensure merging quality;
- Support continuously integration mechanism improvement;
- Regularly review and improve release tasks, from all related aspects, automated processes, tools, processes;
- Manage deployments and environments for QA testing;
- Code branching and merging control.
- Server services management.

1. Proven track record of managing information systems including hardware, software, network, security and IT controls;
2. Experience in managing ERP systems;
3. Familiar with at least one type database (Oracle PLS/QL, Microsoft SQL);
4. Experience in managing installation of IT projects, both small and large;
5. Possess CCNA certification;
6. Self-motivated and proactive in driving continuous improvement.

1) 精通Linux 系統相關知識,有至少三年以上主流Linux (CentOS 6, CentOS 7, Debian等) 使用經驗;
2) 熟悉Linux的高可用性, 集群和分散式系統架構,部署和維護;;
3) 至少熟悉兩種指令碼語言，如GO, Ruby, Shell, Bash, Perl, Python語言等
4) 熟悉Web相關技術，包括Tomcat,Apache,Nginx等開源軟體管理,配置和優化;
5) 熟練掌握資料庫MySQL, Postgres（最好瞭解TSDB）部署,性能調優,高可用;
6) 熟悉VMware, KVM, Docker等;
7) 熟悉Puppet, cfengine, Chef等;
8) 參與項目需求分析, 完成相關系統方案設計
9) 部署和維護開源平臺的軟體和系統和支援現有運營的Linux企業系統
10) 服從領導安排的其他工作, 完成上級領導指定的其他工作任務

Job Description:
Responsibility:
 Participate in the company's network management, planning and implementation; (including firewall, VPN, intrusion detection, etc.) 
 Be responsible for the company's internal information security implementation, and maintenance, And Infrastructure setup 
 Be responsible for TW Office IT related requirement [Svr setup, Storage, Permission Settings, Backup&Restore etc.]
 End-user support  [HelpDesk; Others applications / Svr Room management /PABX, etc]

Candidate Qualification:
MUST HAVE
 Bachelor degree, Minimum 3+ Years of Work experience in same position;
 Familiar with the Windows / Linux operating system, and Permission/rights management; 
 Must have router/Firewall/Switch Configuration experiences. understanding the concept of network security and safety system and related safety equipment; 
 Know Virtualization platform with experience in operation and maintenance;
 Know popular Storage Devices and backup system with experience in operation and maintenance;
 Good at anti-virus sytem, vulnerability scanning, and understand of VPN, IDS, etc.;
 Rich experience in HelpDesk;
 Clear thinking, independent analysis and problem solving ability; 
 Good command in English;
 Have good learning, communication and team cooperation ability.

NICE TO HAVE
 Got Virtualization system setup / maintenance experiences is plus;
 EDA Tools support experiences is plus;
 PABX Maintenance experiences is plus;

基本待遇：
1.試用期薪資為：112,500~186,000p/月（房補15000P、飯補300P/天、2000P/人/月團建費用、1000P/月全勤獎）；轉正後薪資為：139,500~241,000/月（其中15000P為房補、300P/天為飯補、2000P/人/月團建費用、1000P/月為全勤獎）另外享受季度獎金以及年終獎;
2.享受由菲律賓政府頒布的各類公休假以及特別非工作日的假期，工作​​年滿一個自然年（試用期第一天起算），可享有一次15天的帶薪休假，且補助20000P的年假補貼 
3.公司根據菲律賓移民局要求，為員工辦理臨時工簽、工籤等確保員工工作合法性 
4.公司提供菲律賓政府要求的三險（SSS, Philhealth, Pagibig），提供帶薪福利假且給予100000p/次醫療費用報銷 
5.宿舍為酒店式公寓，包菲傭和包乾洗衣物服務，公司自有物業兩層共100套公寓（2017年底建成），提供員工持股機會 
6.公司成立圖書庫, 可以免費借閱, 或是購書, 希望員工藉此提升自我；並提供菲語，英語語言教育訓練，讓員工獲得更多的學習機會 
7.公司持有pagcor牌照，辦理9G工作簽證，保證員工的合法身份


崗位職責：
1，負責公司辦公桌面技術支持，線上緊急故障，疑難問題排查處理;
2，負責Linux，Windows Server服務器的維護及文件備份，Linux，Windows應用程序的配置，管理，升級;
3，負責公司於Linux / Windows服務器的系統升級，擴容需求與資源落實，配合開發需求，測試，調整運維平台;
4，負責制定各服務器的數據備份計劃，並且確保備份數據可用性;
5，負責定期監控各服務器的運行狀態，做出性能分析並問題跟踪;
6，負責抵禦和防止外部病毒，木馬，黑客等對服務器的攻擊，病毒防火牆配置，更新;
7，負責建立和更新相關的操作文檔體系;
如圖8所示，能接受倒班，夜班。

任職要求：
1,  20-30周歲
2，2年以上系統集成/系統運維工作經驗專科及以上學歷，計算機，網絡，通信相關專業畢業;
3，有微軟，redhat，oracle等中高級認證優先考慮。
4，踏實肯幹，謙虛好學，高度的責任感和團隊合作精神。
5，能接受夜班。

技術要求：
1，熟悉的Windows，Linux和UNIX等系統服務和系統管理。
2，了解巴斯，Python和Perl中，PHP等腳本語言。
3 , 了解路由交換，防火牆，上網行為管理，入侵防禦入侵檢測。
4，了解Oracle，MySQL。
5，了解VMWare的，Openstack, Hyper,Citrix，ESX
